==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scurry
<hw>Scur"ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf. <er>Scur</er>,
<er>Skirr</er>.]</ety> <def>To hasten away or along; to move rapidly; to
hurry; <as>as, the rabbit <ex>scurried</ex> away</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scurry</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Scurry
<hw>Scur"ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Act of scurrying; hurried
movement.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scurvily</ent>⟦br⟧
